rComments: Very helpful professor who clearly cares a lot about her students and their well-being. Understanding and will help immensely with projects if you attend office hours. Lectures are insightful and actually interesting to attend. Takes her students opinions regarding course content seriously. One of the nicest professors I've ever had.

Very helpful/friendly professor. Assignments are tough and require in depth thought. Need to attend lecture to do well. For the readings, don't concentrate too much on the text, just come to class and listen to her lecture (she clarifies everything). For the exam and midterm she provides a list of questions and how to do them well.

Really helpful prof, always willing to help in office hours or right after class. Helps clarify assignments and readings and what she expects from students when handing in essays. Overall a fun class to go to, got to watch 2 videos for the entire class, and met up each week for discussion with class mates.
Great Prof, go to office hours will help explain articles and what she looks for in assignments. Always willing to help!
